data.title: What's on ICC.tv
data.text:
Here you’ll find the list of tournaments, series and matches that are available to be live-streamed within your region throughout the year!

With a variety of match highlights, ICC films and documentaries, you can browse the ICC’s extensive library of on-demand videos.

Here’s what you can watch LIVE and FREE on ICC.tv in 2024:

August

ICC CWC League 2 - Netherlands

ICC Men's T20 World Cup EAP Sub-Regional Qualifier A

ICC Men's T20 World Cup Europe Sub-Regional Qualifier C

September

ICC Men's T20 World Cup Asia Sub-Regional Qualifier A

UAE & Zimbabwe Women's Tour of Namibia

ICC CWC League 2 - Namibia

ICC CWC League 2 - Canada

ICC Men's T20 World Cup EAP Sub-Regional Qualifier B

October

ICC Women's T20 World Cup Bangladesh 2024

Not an ICC Family member yet? Sign up here.

ICC CWC League 2 - Netherlands

The qualification road to the 2027 ICC Cricket World Cup resumes with the fourth round of the ICC CWC League 2 taking place in the Netherlands. Canada, Netherlands and the USA will contest for points, with this being the first outing for the USA who have been keen observers so far in the cycle.

Matches:

11 August, Netherlands v Canada, 9:00

13 August, Canada v USA, 9:00

15 August, Netherlands v USA, 9:00

17 August, Canada v Netherlands, 9:00

19 August, USA v Canada, 9:00

21 August, USA v Netherlands, 9:00

All timings are UTC.

Available Territories:

Worldwide except Afghanistan, Bangladesh, Bhutan, India, Maldives, Myanmar, Nepal, Pakistan, Sri Lanka.

ICC CWC League 2 - Namibia

The qualification road to the 2027 ICC Cricket World Cup resumes with the fifth round of the ICC CWC League 2, with Namibia hosting the UAE and USA. In the USA's second outing of the cycle, they and the UAE will be vying for crucial points.

Matches:

16 September, Namibia v USA, TBC

18 September, UAE v USA, TBC

20 September, Namibia v UAE, TBC

22 September, USA v Namibia, TBC

24 September, USA v UAE, TBC

26 September, UAE v Namibia, TBC

All timings will be UTC.

Available Territories:

Worldwide except Afghanistan, Bangladesh, Bhutan, India, Maldives, Myanmar, Nepal, Pakistan, Sri Lanka.

ICC CWC League 2 - Canada

The qualification road to the 2027 ICC Cricket World Cup resumes with the sixth round of the ICC CWC League 2. Canada, Nepal and Oman will face off, with Nepal in search of wins to regain some of the ground they may have lost from a lackluster start, but history suggests the side can make up ground in a hurry with a young group boasting immense potential.

Matches:

16 September, Canada v Oman, 14:00

18 September, Canada v Nepal, 14:00

20 September, Nepal v Oman, 14:00

22 September, Oman v Canada, 14:00

24 September, Oman v Nepal, 14:00

26 September, Nepal v Canada, 14:00

All timings are UTC.

Available Territories:

Worldwide except Afghanistan, Bangladesh, Bhutan, India, Maldives, Myanmar, Nepal, Pakistan, Sri Lanka.
